        <div class="form-group col-md-offset-2 col-md-8 e-sub"><input type="submit" class="btn-sub" value="Submit" /></div>
    
</div>
<div class="row">
    <p class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10">STB Chain (STB) is currently the world’s leading application of Blockchain technology in software, and is a decentralised, tamper-proof and completely traceable rights verification trading system. STB covers multi-field technology applications, a few examples being Cloud Computing, Big Data, AI and SaaS cloud services. Scientific and technological achievement-based. Our goal is to establish a new ecosystem of distributed application software services with no borders. With the combination of Blockchain technology and the software industry, an effective copyright protection and trading platform will be established.
    </p>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    <script src="~/Scripts/telegram.js"></script>
}

